<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Chatchawal Pump</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Prompt:wght@300;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
body {
    font-family: 'Prompt', sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    background: #f8fafc;
    color: #1e293b;
}

/* NAVBAR */
nav {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.85);
    color: white;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 15px 30px;
    z-index: 1000;
}
nav a {
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin: 0 10px;
}

/* HERO */
.hero {
    height: 90vh;
    background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.6), rgba(0,0,0,0.6)),
    url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581092580497-e0d23cbdf1dc');
    background-size: cover;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
}
.hero h1 {
    font-size: 48px;
}
.hero p {
    font-size: 20px;
}
.cta {
    margin-top:20px;
    padding:15px 30px;
    background:#00b4d8;
    border:none;
    font-size:18px;
    color:white;
    border-radius:10px;
    cursor:pointer;
}

/* SECTION */
section {
    padding: 60px 20px;
    text-align: center;
}

/* FEATURES */
.features {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 20px;
}
.feature {
    width: 250px;
    background:white;
    padding:20px;
    border-radius:10px;
    box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

/* PRODUCTS */
.products {
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
    gap:20px;
}
.card {
    background:white;
    padding:20px;
    border-radius:12px;
    box-shadow:0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}
.card img {
    width:100%;
    border-radius:10px;
}
.price {
    color:#0077b6;
    font-size:20px;
}
.buy {
    margin-top:10px;
    display:inline-block;
    padding:10px 20px;
    background:#0077b6;
    color:white;
    border-radius:6px;
    text-decoration:none;
}

/* TESTIMONIAL */
.testimonial {
    background:#e0f2fe;
    padding:40px;
    border-radius:10px;
    max-width:600px;
    margin:auto;
}

/* FOOTER */
footer {
    background:#020617;
    color:white;
    padding:20px;
}

/* LINE FLOAT */
.line {
    position:fixed;
    bottom:20px;
    right:20px;
    background:#06c755;
    color:white;
    padding:15px;
    border-radius:50%;
    font-size:20px;
    text-decoration:none;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<nav>
    <div><strong>Chatchawal Pump</strong></div>
    <div>
        <a href="#">หน้าแรก</a>
        <a href="#products">สินค้า</a>
        <a href="#contact">ติดต่อ</a>
    </div>
</nav>

<div class="hero">
    <h1>ปั๊มน้ำคุณภาพสูง</h1>
    <p>แรง ทน คุ้มค่า สำหรับทุกการใช้งาน</p>
    <button class="cta" onclick="location.href='#products'">ดูสินค้า</button>
</div>

<section>
    <h2>ทำไมต้องเลือกเรา?</h2>
    <div class="features">
        <div class="feature">💧 คุณภาพสูง</div>
        <div class="feature">⚡ แรงดันดี</div>
        <div class="feature">🛠 รับประกัน</div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="products">
    <h2>สินค้าแนะนำ</h2>
    <div class="products">

        <div class="card">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1565043666747-69f6646db940">
            <h3>ปั๊มน้ำบ้าน</h3>
            <p class="price">3,500 บาท</p>
            <a class="buy" href="#">สั่งซื้อ</a>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581092918056-0c4c3acd3789">
            <h3>ปั๊มอุตสาหกรรม</h3>
            <p class="price">7,900 บาท</p>
            <a class="buy" href="#">สั่งซื้อ</a>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<section>
    <h2>รีวิวลูกค้า</h2>
    <div class="testimonial">
        “ของดีมาก ใช้งานทน แรงดันน้ำดีขึ้นชัดเจน”
    </div>
</section>

<section id="contact">
    <h2>ติดต่อเรา</h2>
    <p>📞 08X-XXX-XXXX</p>
    <p>📧 your@email.com</p>
</section>

<a href="https://line.me" class="line">LINE</a>

<footer>
    © 2026 Chatchawal Pump
</footer>

</body>
</html>
